<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">FTX Trading Ltd., Sam Bankman-Fried=E2=80=99s =
bankrupt crypto exchange, has been under new management since filing for ba=
nkruptcy last November,<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-4" sty=
le=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width=
: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; =
background-color: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[4]</span>
</a>=C2=A0and the new managers have two related but distinct jobs. One job =
is to maximize the recovery of the bankruptcy estate: They have to round up=
 all of FTX=E2=80=99s assets, sell them for as much money as possible, and =
give the money to FTX=E2=80=99s creditors (meaning mostly its customers). T=
he other job=C2=A0is to explain what went wrong to land FTX =E2=80=94=C2=A0=
which a week before filing for bankruptcy looked like a large, stable and s=
uccessful crypto exchange =E2=80=94=C2=A0in bankruptcy. The explaining itse=
lf might help maximize recovery =E2=80=94=C2=A0if the explanation of what w=
ent wrong is =E2=80=9Cprior management stole the money,=E2=80=9D the bankru=
ptcy estate can sue the prior managers to get the money back =E2=80=94=C2=
=A0though that is not its only purpose. It can also help=C2=A0<em>prosecute=
 </em>prior management, and provide a certain emotional and intellectual cl=
osure.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Yesterday <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombe=
rgbusiness.com/click/30288429.269516/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cucHJuZXdzd2lyZS5jb20vbm=
V3cy1yZWxlYXNlcy9mdHgtZGVidG9ycy1wcm92aWRlLWFkZGl0aW9uYWwtaW5mb3JtYXRpb24td=
