ef4b8524a319a23cB3114609b" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" t=
arget=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important;=
 border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-styl=
e: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> FTX</a>=C2=A0=E2=80=9Cannounced that th=
eir top level management and advisors met with the members of and advisors =
to the Official Committee of Unsecured Creditors=E2=80=9D to give the credi=
tors an update on what they have found. Here is <a href=3D"https://link.mai=
l.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30288429.269516/aHR0cHM6Ly9yZXN0cnVjdHVyaW5nL=
nJhLmtyb2xsLmNvbS9GVFgvSG9tZS1Eb3dubG9hZFBERj9pZDE9TVRRek9EVTFOUSUzRCUzRCZp=
