<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;"><a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness=
.com/click/30288429.269516/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubnl0aW1lcy5jb20vMjAyMy8wMS8xNC9i=
dXNpbmVzcy9kZWFsYm9vay9ob3ctY29tbW9uLWlzLWNvcnBvcmF0ZS1mcmF1ZC5odG1sP3NtaWQ=
